snippet.title: //TODO: today - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
It's finally time! We have a release date °˖ ✧◝(○ ヮ ○)◜✧˖ °
The full version of //TODO: today will be released on September 28th 2018!
As before you will be able to download the game for free on itch.io and you will also be able to purchase a special edition with a bonus zine and the soundtrack!

To stay up to date on our games and their development, follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/boyslaughplus
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/boyslaugh.plus/
Or take a look at our website: http://boyslaughplus.moe
